snippet.title: Impulse Rouge - 4 Minutes of Gameplay - Steam Demo version
snippet.description:
In the fight between the Light Spirit Council and the High Dark Spirits, you are a young spirit who decided to start their own path fighting demons, to discover that everything from the start is against something else entirely.

Link To Steam Store: https://steam.pm/app/1910800

Visit The Official Website: https://impulse.neithowl.com

#gaming #impulserogue #gamescom
